EffectLib is licensed under the MIT License.

This directory contains a vendored, locally-maintained fork of EffectLib
(https://github.com/elBukkit/EffectLib), based on the upstream 10.3 release,
with local additions and modifications (e.g. OriginalEffect, FireworkEffect,
and per-effect tweaks). It is bundled and maintained in-tree for CrateReloaded.

